Package edu.calvin.cs262.prototype.activities

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    BlueprintActivity
    BlueprintActivity Utilizes a web view to retrieve and display images of the floorplans that exist on an external server.
    DestActivity
    Destination Activity

    Allows user to enter building and (optional) room number in the text fields then brings user to Map Activity upon pressing Go! button.
    MainActivity
    Main Menu Activity Contains buttons for accessing both the Map and Destination Activities along with our help document
    MapsActivity
    MapsActivity models an Android activity to display Google Maps in order to view your location at Calvin.
